entries.title_d: Remain in the Endor system and drop off the Rebel data to a command shuttle. They are sending the shuttle to pick up the plans from you.
entries.title: Endor System: Dropoff the Rebel Data
entries.split_quest_alert: Initiate patrol route. Keep a watch out for suspicious and especially rebellious activity. Destroy any command vessels located in the area.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the supplied Nav waypoint and wait for the shuttle to arrive.
entries.quest_location_d: The shuttle will meet you in the Endor system.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the shuttle and transfer the Rebel data to it.
entries.hello_d: I see you, pilot. We will begin the uplink procedure as soon as we finish our jump.
entries.found_loc_d: Please proceed to the following location and stand by for arrival of HQ command shuttle.
entries.failed_destroyed: You allowed your transfer shuttle to be destroyed? That was an expensive ship. You are going to have to answer to your commander about this failure.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Beginning uplink procedure. Please stand by.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Data transfer completed. Be safe out there, pilot.
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:\#pcontrast3 <Enemy fighters detected on an intercept course.>
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Wait for the arrival of the command shuttle to retrieve the data.
